OL,3,CVapes containing spice sold to
OL,4,Cchildren on TikTok and Instagram
OL,6,FSome TikTok and Instagram accounts are
OL,7,Fbeing used to sell vapes containing
OL,8,Fthe synthetic drug 'spice' to
OL,9,Fchildren, researchers from the
OL,10,FUniversity of Bath have found.
OL,12,FLast summer, ITV News West Country
OL,13,Fexclusively revealed that vapes were
OL,14,Fbeing laced with THC, which is a
OL,15,Fcompound from the cannabis plant, and
OL,16,Fspice, a man-made drug originally
OL,17,Fdesigned to mimic the effects of
OL,18,Fcannabis.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G1/15
