OL,3,CVapes containing spice sold to
OL,4,Cchildren on TikTok and Instagram
OL,6,FUp to one in four vapes confiscated in
OL,7,Fsecondary schools in England now
OL,8,Fcontain the synthetic drug "spice", a
OL,9,Fstudy has found.
OL,11,FResearchers from the University of
OL,12,FBath analysed 1,923 e-cigarettes and e-
OL,13,Fliquids, collected from 114 schools
OL,14,Facross seven regions in England.
OL,16,FThey found spice in 13% of overall
OL,17,Fsamples but in two areas, London and
OL,18,FLancashire, this figure rose to around
OL,19,F25%.
OL,26,@pD@\OUpD@bO]
