OL,3,CVapes containing spice sold to
OL,4,Cchildren on TikTok and Instagram
OL,6,FThe study, led by Professor Chris
OL,7,FPudney from the university's
OL,8,FDepartment of Life Sciences, also
OL,9,Ffound that spice-laced vapes are
OL,10,Feasily available online.
OL,12,FVapes are often marked as containing
OL,13,FTHC ` the active ingredient in
OL,14,Fcannabis ` despite actually containing
OL,15,Fspice, a more dangerous and cheaper
OL,16,Fsubstance.
OL,18,FResearchers surveyed online accounts
OL,19,Fon Facebook, Instagram and TikTok over
OL,20,Fa three-month period, tracking those
OL,21,Fpurporting to sell THC vapes.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/15
