OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax     F433A1757094110
OL,3,CVapes containing spice sold to
OL,4,Cchildren on TikTok and Instagram
OL,6,FThey found that as the demographic of
OL,7,Fsocial media platforms becomes
OL,8,Fyounger, more of the e-liquids
OL,9,Fmarketed as THC are likely to be spice
OL,10,F` with 12% of these for Facebook
OL,11,Fcompared to 68% for TikTok.
OL,13,FThe University of Bath said this
OL,14,Fmirrored real-world data, with only
OL,15,F1.2% of vapes and e-liquids
OL,16,Fconfiscated in schools containing THC
OL,17,Fand 13% containing spice.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G4/15
