OL,4,Cchildren on TikTok and Instagram
OL,6,FProf Pudney said: "Spice e-liquids are
OL,7,Ftrivially available on social media
OL,8,Flike TikTok and Instagram, with
OL,9,Fapparent drug dealing on these
OL,10,Fplatforms.
OL,12,F"A simple search of social media
OL,13,Fplatforms brings up hundreds of
OL,14,Faccounts selling this material, making
OL,15,Fthem incredibly easy for young people
OL,16,Fto find.
OL,26,@nD@SOUtD@AOU
