OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax     F433A1757094110
OL,3,CVapes containing spice sold to
OL,4,Cchildren on TikTok and Instagram
OL,6,F"Spice is much cheaper than THC. Young
OL,7,Fpeople think they're buying a cannabis
OL,8,Fproduct but instead they're being
OL,9,Fpushed a highly addictive, cheap drug
OL,10,Fwith unpredictable and serious health
OL,11,Feffects, such as psychosis, seizures
OL,12,Fand heart problems."
OL,14,FThe report's authors are calling for
OL,15,FOfcom ` the media and communications
OL,16,Fregulator for the UK ` to open an
OL,17,Fenforcement programme for online drug
OL,18,Fsales.
OL,26,@nD@AOUtD@TO]
