OL,3,CVapes containing spice sold to
OL,4,Cchildren on TikTok and Instagram
OL,6,FUnder the Online Safety Act, social
OL,7,Fmedia platforms are expected to assess
OL,8,Fthe risk that their services could be
OL,9,Fused to sell or promote illegal drugs.
OL,11,FOfcom can issue fines of up to #18
OL,12,Fmillion or 10% of a company's global
OL,13,Fannual revenue, whichever is greater,
OL,14,Fagainst companies which do not follow
OL,15,Ftheir duties.
OL,17,FProf Pudney added: "The Online Safety
OL,18,FAct needs to be used to compel social
OL,19,Fmedia companies to find and remove the
OL,20,Faccounts selling these drugs to
OL,21,Fchildren.
OL,26,@yD@TOU
