OL,3,CVapes containing spice sold to
OL,4,Cchildren on TikTok and Instagram
OL,6,F"We are calling for Ofcom to be
OL,7,Fproperly resourced and directed to
OL,8,Fopen a specific enforcement programme
OL,9,Fdedicated to online drug sales.
OL,11,F"People who use spice are at high risk
OL,12,Fof coercion and abuse by drug dealers.
OL,13,FThis is a failure of online safety
OL,14,Fthat is causing direct harm to
OL,15,Fchildren."
OL,17,FThe study, conducted between June and
OL,18,FAugust this year, identified 120
OL,19,FTikTok accounts and 83 Instagram
OL,20,Faccounts offering vapes described as
OL,21,Fcontaining THC for sale.
OL,26,@nD@AOUsD@AOUwD@JO]
