OL,3,CVapes containing spice sold to
OL,4,Cchildren on TikTok and Instagram
OL,6,FThis is despite THC being a controlled
OL,7,Fsubstance in the UK.
OL,9,FResearchers used their analysis of
OL,10,Fvapes and e-liquids from schools to
OL,11,Fvisually triage online images of spice-
OL,12,Fcontaining e-liquids online.
OL,14,FThis visual analysis found nearly 70%
OL,15,Fof TikTok accounts and more than 50%
OL,16,Fof Instagram accounts claiming to sell
OL,17,FTHC were actually selling spice.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G9/15
