OL,6,FIn March 2025, researchers made social
OL,7,Fmedia companies aware of the issue
OL,8,Fthrough the Drugs on Social Media
OL,9,Fworking group.
OL,11,F"We're holding companies to account" -
OL,12,FOfcom
OL,14,FHowever, as of September 1, around 70%
OL,15,Fof accounts tracked by researchers
OL,16,Fremain online and easily accessible
OL,17,Fthrough keyword searches, they said.
OL,19,FProf Pudney said: "We have clearly
OL,20,Fdetailed this issue to the major
OL,21,Fsocial media companies.
