OL,6,F"About 70% of accounts that we have
OL,7,Fidentified and tracked are still
OL,8,Fonline and easily accessible. The
OL,9,Fresponse of these platforms appears
OL,10,Finsufficient to tackle this urgent
OL,11,Fissue."
OL,13,FFiona Spargo-Mabbs, who chairs the
OL,14,FDrugs on Social Media working group,
OL,15,Fis the founder of drug education
OL,16,Fcharity the Daniel Spargo-Mabbs
OL,17,FFoundation.
