OL,6,FShe said: "As we start another
OL,7,Facademic year, we're very concerned
OL,8,Fthat we're going to see increased use
OL,9,F` and increased harm from the use ` of
OL,10,Fspice by teenagers, as a result of the
OL,11,Fongoing visibility of vapes being sold
OL,12,Fas THC on their social media platforms.
OL,14,F"This important research has clearly
OL,15,Fshown that until this is adequately
OL,16,Faddressed, young people will continue
OL,17,Fto be exposed to potentially
OL,18,Fsignificant risk from this potent
OL,19,Fsubstance, to an extent we haven't
OL,20,Fseen before."
