OL,6,FA spokesperson for Ofcom said: "Under
OL,7,Fthe Online Safety Act, social media
OL,8,Fplatforms must remove criminal content
OL,9,Fquickly when they become aware of it `
OL,10,Fincluding activity which amounts to an
OL,11,Fillegal offer to supply drugs ` and
OL,12,Ftake appropriate steps to reduce the
OL,13,Frisk of UK users seeing it in the
OL,14,Ffirst place.
OL,16,F"We're holding companies to account `
OL,17,Fwe've already launched investigations
OL,18,Finto 47 sites and apps, and expect to
OL,19,Fannounce more in the coming months.
